commit.message:
MAINTAINERS: Change spelling from "fortran 95" to "Fortran".

	* MAINTAINERS: Change spelling from "fortran 95" to "Fortran".
	Move all Fortran maintainers except Paul Brook into the
	Non-Autopoiesis section.
